ttp_template:
<group name="hour_last_ntp_sync_minute_second">
current time is: {{HOUR}}:{{MINUTE}}:{{SECOND | ORPHRASE}}
last ntp sync: {{LAST_NTP_SYNC | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
current time is: 21:05:34
last ntp sync: never
textfsm_template:
Value HOUR (\d{2})
Value MINUTE (\d{2})
Value SECOND (\d{2})
Value LAST_NTP_SYNC (.*?)

Start
  ^\s*current\s+time\s+is:\s+${HOUR}:${MINUTE}:${SECOND}\s*$$
  ^\s*last\s+ntp\s+sync:\s+${LAST_NTP_SYNC}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
